Item 2.02. Results of Operations and Financial Condition.
 
On January 24, 2005, Altera Corporation issued a press release announcing its financial results for the fourth quarter of 2004. A copy of the press release is furnished as Exhibit 99.1 to this report.
 
Item 9.01. Financial Statements and Exhibits.
 
 
 
 
 
