2. . As used herein, the following definitions shall apply:
Definitions
 
(a) "" means the Board or any Committees as shall be administering the Plan, in accordance with Section 4 of the Plan.
Administrator
 
(b) "" means the legal requirements relating to the administration of stock option plans under U. S. state corporate laws, U.S. federal and state securities laws, the Code and the applicable laws of any foreign country or jurisdiction where Options are, or will be, granted under the Plan.
