Altera Corporation (NASDAQ: ALTR) today announced that, based on quarter-to-date results and the company's outlook for the remainder of the quarter, first quarter revenue is now expected to be up 7 to 10 percent sequentially. The company's previous guidance was for sequential growth of 5 to 10 percent.
