ALTERA ANNOUNCES FOURTH QUARTER RESULTS
San Jose, Calif
., January 24, 2012  Altera Corporation (NASDAQ: ALTR) today announced fourth quarter sales of
$457.8 million
, down
12 percent
from the third quarter of 2011 and down
18 percent
from the fourth quarter of 2010. Fourth quarter net income was
$146.6 million
,
$0.45
per diluted share, compared with net income of
$185.4 million
,
$0.57
per diluted share, in the third quarter of 2011 and
$231.6 million
,
$0.72
per diluted share, in the fourth quarter of 2010.
